                Arlington, home to world-class sports venues and entertainment destinations, is a vibrant hub of tourism and commerce in North Texas. From the iconic AT&T Stadium and Globe Life Field to the dynamic Texas Live! entertainment complex, your business environment reflects Arlington's commitment to excellence and hospitality.
              </p>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-700 mb-6">
                Dream Cleaned understands the unique cleaning challenges of Arlington businesses. Whether you're in the Entertainment District, the University area, or the thriving business corridors, we provide tailored cleaning solutions that maintain the high standards your customers and employees expect in this dynamic city.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg border-l-4 border-brand-gold self-start">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why Arlington Businesses Choose<br>Dream Cleaned</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                  <CheckCircle className="h-4 w-4 text-brand-gold mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Local expertise in Arlington business districts</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
